#: ../../J/jibble.rst:5
msgid "jibble"
msgstr "jibble"

#: ../../J/jibble.rst:7
msgid ""
"[UK] Unspecified stuff. An unspecified action. A deliberately blank word; "
"compare :ref:`gorets`\\. A deliberate experiment in tracking the spread of a"
" near-meaningless word. See `http://www.jibble.org/jibblemeaning.php "
"<http://www.jibble.org/jibblemeaning.php>`_."
msgstr ""
"[英国] 何だか分からないもの。何だか分からない行為。意図的に空白にされた語。\\ :ref:`gorets`\\ "
"と比較せよ。ほとんど無意味な語の広まり方を追跡する意図的な実験。\\ `http://www.jibble.org/jibblemeaning.php "
"<http://www.jibble.org/jibblemeaning.php>`_ を参照。"
